          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p dir="ltr">The Nintendo Switch Pro Controller has finally received an official, substantial discount for <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/black-friday/">Black Friday</a>. It only took seven-plus years for it to happen, but if you've exercised extreme patience, you have finally been rewarded. The <a href="https://howl.link/4u89rix4xiw5t?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320320146702?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch Pro Controller is on sale for $20 off at Best Buy</a>, dropping the price from $70 down to $50. Needless to say, this is the best discount ever on the official Switch controller, so we wouldn't be surprised to see this offer sell out before Black Friday sales end.</p><p dir="ltr">You can also save $20 on a pair of Neon Red and Blue Joy-Con Controllers. And if you're in the market for a Nintendo Switch console this holiday, Target and Best Buy have ridiculously good deals on the Nintendo Switch holiday bundles. You can get the <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fnintendo-switch-oled-model-mario-kart-8-deluxe-bundle%2F-%2FA-93089489&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnintendo-switch-pro-controller-is-only-50-for-black-friday-lowest-price-ever%2F1100-6527850%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch OLED Mario Kart bundle for only $275</a></strong> or the <strong><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fnintendo-switch-mario-kart-8-deluxe-bundle%2F-%2FA-93089490&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnintendo-switch-pro-controller-is-only-50-for-black-friday-lowest-price-ever%2F1100-6527850%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">regular Nintendo Switch Mario Kart bundle for only $225</a></strong>.</p><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/7zxgr792p2cpm?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324286330385?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch hardware deals at Best Buy</a></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/p10qq4ee1wfi8?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324290882125?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch game deals at Best Buy</a></li></ul><div title="6527850 - Switch Pro Black Friday 2024 deal" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="2858" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6527850 - Switch Pro Black Friday 2024 deal" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://howl.link/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320291104429?u1=subid_value" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/howl.link\/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/17320291104429?u1=subid_value&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://howl.link/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320291104429?u1=subid_value">Nintendo Switch Pro Controller</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://howl.link/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320291104429?u1=subid_value" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/howl.link\/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/17320291104429?u1=subid_value&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://howl.link/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320291104429?u1=subid_value">$50 (was $70)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p dir="ltr">The Nintendo Switch Pro Controller remains our top pick on our <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-nintendo-switch-controller/1100-6469264/" data-ref-id="1100-6469264">best Switch controllers</a> list all these years later. It's significantly better for docked play than slotting two controllers in the Joy-Con Grip. It also has chunkier face buttons, full-size analog sticks, and larger triggers. It also has a real D-pad, which is a big plus when compared to Joy-Con Controllers.</p><p dir="ltr">The Switch Pro Controller is equipped with Nintendo's HD rumble, gyro sensors for motion controls, and has an NFC reader to tap Nintendo's Amiibo figures. Since it's a Bluetooth controller, the Pro Controller also works great on PC, Mac, mobile, Steam Deck, and several other devices. It charges via USB-C and runs for up to 40 hours on a full battery.</p><p dir="ltr">The Pro Controller is a great all-around controller with superb ergonomics. It rivals the Xbox Wireless Controller for the title of comfiest controller with offset sticks.</p><p dir="ltr">The Switch Pro Controller Black Friday deal is currently available at <a href="https://howl.link/ov5dsi0s6mu4d?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320291104429?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Best Buy</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.target.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F81938%2F2092%3FsubId1%3Dsubid_value%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fnintendo-switch-pro-controller%2F-%2FA-52180631&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnintendo-switch-pro-controller-is-only-50-for-black-friday-lowest-price-ever%2F1100-6527850%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Target</a>. <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FNintendo-Switch-Pro-Controller%2F55485228%26subId1%3Dsubid_value&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnintendo-switch-pro-controller-is-only-50-for-black-friday-lowest-price-ever%2F1100-6527850%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Walmart</a> will also have this deal starting November 25.</p></div>                      </div><p dir="ltr">As mentioned, the <a href="https://howl.link/8tux5sakxv8mw?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/1732428545438?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Switch</a> and <a href="https://howl.link/5hr9n4pxnb6xq?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324285360171?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Switch OLED holiday bundles</a> are up for grabs for $75 off. Both consoles come bundled with Mario Kart 8 Deluxe and a 12-Month Nintendo Switch Online membership. You're getting $80 worth of "freebies" with each, which is why the holiday bundles typically don't receive outright discounts during Black Friday. These are the best Nintendo Switch deals ever offered by a major retailer.</p><hr><p dir="ltr">A nice selection of first-party Nintendo games is on sale for Black Friday, too. A trio of Mario platformers have received substantial discounts. Most notably, you can get <a href="https://howl.link/0qo5vdwx5hqiq?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320299749294?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Super Mario Odyssey</a> for only $30. <a href="https://howl.link/tjhf13dxx2f8z?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324062738691?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom</a>'s $40 price is a new all-time low. The cozy sim <a href="https://howl.link/pf34b845rd8vt?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320308003428?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Animal Crossing: New Horizons</a> rarely receives discounts, so this $20 price cut is definitely worth checking out. This is also the first time the remastered collection of the first two Pikmin games has been discounted, so snag <a href="https://howl.link/nvywiuy5pgfcf?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17321154925959?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Pikmin 1 + 2</a> for $30 before it's gone.</p><h2><strong>Nintendo Black Friday Deals</strong></h2><h3><strong>Nintendo Switch games</strong></h3><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/pf34b845rd8vt?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17320308003428?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Animal Crossing: New Horizons</a> -- $40 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/tjhf13dxx2f8z?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324062738691?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom</a> -- $40 (<del>$70</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/jisxyqsjxl28h?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324063990155?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Kirby and the Forgotten Land</a> -- $40 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/g9h06iqmut012?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324065395715?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch Sports</a> -- $40 (<del>$50</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/nvywiuy5pgfcf?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17321154925959?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Pikmin 1 + 2</a> -- $30 (<del>$50</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/8cv7ibeh5io6u?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/1732406685131?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Pikmin 4</a> -- $40 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/9knu5nfwuqrot?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324287737719?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Super Mario 3D World + Bowser's Fury</a> -- $40 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://howl.link/hk6wtvsowzqxb?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17324068684157?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow